frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers on a lemon tart, appearing to work on the dessert as if it were a construction site. The tart is adorned with lemon slices and zest, while powdered sugar is being sprinkled from above. Ladders are placed around the tart, adding to the playful illusion of a work site.
frames.description: The scene is a creative and playful setup where tiny figurines of construction workers are positioned on a lemon tart, giving the impression of a miniature construction project. The setting is bright and sunny, with a focus on the dessert and the tiny figures.
